# Design Decisions — {{BRAND_NAME}}

Log of architectural and design decisions. Record the WHY, not just the what.

---

## Format

```
### [Short title]
**Date:** YYYY-MM-DD
**Decision:** What was decided
**Why:** The reason — constraint, tradeoff, or explicit preference
**Alternatives considered:** What was rejected and why
```

---

### Initial setup

**Date:** {{YEAR}}-01-01
**Decision:** Next.js 14 App Router + TypeScript strict + Tailwind CSS
**Why:** App Router gives streaming SSR for LCP; TypeScript eliminates runtime trial-error loops with AI; Tailwind with token mapping enforces design system mechanically.
**Alternatives considered:** Astro (rejected: less flexible for forms/interactivity); plain CSS (rejected: no design-token enforcement at build time).

